data.title: Ladder Up
data.text:
9th Annual Tee Up Golf Outing

Monday, September 23, 2024 | 9 AM

Register and Sponsorship

Join Ladder Up’s 9th Annual Tee Up, a day of golf, fun, and philanthropy! This event is an opportunity to enjoy a round and benefit Ladder Up’s mission to empower individuals and families in the Chicagoland area toward financial stability.

Whether you’re an avid golfer or a beginner, come out and join us for a memorable day on the greens. Tickets are also available to join the post-golf cocktail reception.

Please email Kristy Kotek, Director of Development, at kkotek@goladderup.org for information on Tee Up, sponsorship, and in-kind opportunities.

2024 Bank of America Chicago Marathon

Sunday, October 13, 2024

Ladder Up is an official charity partner of the 2024 Bank of America Chicago Marathon.

We are proud to introduce our inaugural running team who will lace up and run the 26.2 miles on behalf of Ladder Up this year!

Make a donation today! All proceeds directly benefit our mission.

16th Annual Casino Night & Silent Auction

Friday, May 17 | 7 – 11PM

Join Ladder Up’s 16th Annual Casino Night & Silent Auction. Enjoy casino games, bid on exclusive items in our silent auction, and indulge in cocktails & hors d’oeuvres, all while enjoying live music and mingling with fellow supporters.

All proceeds benefit Ladder Up’s mission to empower individuals and families in the Chicagoland area toward financial stability.

Get your tickets now and join us for a night of fun and philanthropy!

Please consider sponsoring the event to demonstrate your commitment to the hardworking clients Ladder Up serves. Please email Kristy Kotek, Director of Development, at kkotek@goladderup.org for more information on Casino Night, sponsorship, and in-kind opportunities.
